spec_data.Name: php-pear-Pager
spec_data.Description:
It takes an array of data as input and pages it according to various
parameters. It also builds links within a specified range, and allows
complete customization of the output (it even works with front controllers
and mod_rewrite). Two operating modes available: "Jumping" and "Sliding"
window style.
